"{\"uid\": \"cityam.com-how-samsung-pampers-and-nbc-struck-gold-at-paris-2024-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Featured  Submit a story  Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 45, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Featured  Submit a story  Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 47, \"to\": 92, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Featured  Submit a story  Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 94, \"to\": 139, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"By:Louise Johnson  CEO of Fuse - Fuse  The Paris 2024 Olympics marked a cultural shift in how brands connect with global audiences, with the games being dubbed the \\\"TikTok Olympics\\\" due to many sponsors' digital-first approach.\", \"from\": 141, \"to\": 368, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 144, \"end\": 158, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louise_Johnson\", \"score\": 0.9999999995534381, \"rank\": 4.463609449245187e-10, \"text\": \"Louise Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louise_Johnson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louise_Johnson\"}, {\"begin\": 167, \"end\": 171, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/808_Mafia\", \"score\": 0.9999999986557668, \"rank\": 1.3375607405561446e-09, \"text\": \"Fuse\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/808_Mafia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/808_Mafia\"}, {\"begin\": 174, \"end\": 178, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/808_Mafia\", \"score\": 0.9999999986557668, \"rank\": 1.3375607405561446e-09, \"text\": \"Fuse\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/808_Mafia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/808_Mafia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As the International Olympic Committee (IOC) acknowledges an ageing fanbase-the average age has risen by approximately 10 years in just a decade-the need to captivate younger consumers has never been more pressing.\", \"from\": 370, \"to\": 584, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 377, \"end\": 414, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 377, \"end\": 414, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This urgency has driven brands to rethink their strategies, moving towards innovative campaigns that blend cultural relevance, human stories, and digital engagement.\", \"from\": 586, \"to\": 751, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Samsung emerged as one of the most prominent brands at the Paris 2024 Games, successfully capitalising on the event's global reach.\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 884, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 753, \"end\": 760, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"score\": 0.9999999951623977, \"rank\": 4.8377783380414496e-09, \"text\": \"Samsung\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Through their \\\"Team Samsung Galaxy\\\" initiative, the brand not only highlighted the talents of both debut and returning athletes but also bridged the gap between the online and offline experiences.\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 1081, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Their clever use of \\\"victory selfies\\\" taken on their latest flip smartphone, which was gifted to all 17,000 competitors, ensured that the product became a focal point in the games' digital narrative.\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1282, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These images significantly boosted sales for Samsung's foldable phone, with a notable 23 per cent increase following key victories by Team GB athletes.\", \"from\": 1283, \"to\": 1434, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1328, \"end\": 1335, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"score\": 0.9999999951623977, \"rank\": 4.8377783380414496e-09, \"text\": \"Samsung\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stay in the game with The Turnover: your weekly roundup of sport business news, expert analysis and behind\\u2011the\\u2011scenes stories from City\\u202fAM's sports desk.\", \"from\": 1436, \"to\": 1589, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The campaign's success underscored the power of integrating product placement with real-time social media amplification, setting a new benchmark for how to activate Olympic sponsorship rights.\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1783, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Relaxed IOC rules at Paris 2024 also allowed for more direct, unfiltered athlete-to-fan interactions - a move that brands were quick to leverage.\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1930, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pampers, in particular, made a lasting impact by partnering with track and field star Allyson Felix to highlight the first-ever Olympic Village nursery.\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 2083, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2017, \"end\": 2030, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allyson_Felix\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Allyson Felix\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allyson_Felix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allyson_Felix\"}, {\"begin\": 2059, \"end\": 2074, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 0.9999999999863576, \"rank\": 1.3523623124999561e-11, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This collaboration was a powerful statement on the compatibility of motherhood and athletic excellence.\", \"from\": 2085, \"to\": 2188, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The nursery's presence addressed a long-overlooked need and aligned perfectly with Pampers' brand values.\", \"from\": 2189, \"to\": 2294, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2272, \"end\": 2279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pampers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pampers\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pampers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pampers\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Felix's personal story, coupled with Pampers' commitment, resonated deeply with audiences, especially considering Felix's previous conflicts with Nike after becoming a mother.\", \"from\": 2296, \"to\": 2471, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2296, \"end\": 2301, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Felix_Mendelssohn\", \"score\": 0.9999990018718997, \"rank\": 9.980603115140778e-07, \"text\": \"Felix\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Felix_Mendelssohn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Felix_Mendelssohn\"}, {\"begin\": 2333, \"end\": 2340, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pampers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pampers\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pampers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pampers\"}, {\"begin\": 2410, \"end\": 2415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Felix_Mendelssohn\", \"score\": 0.9999990018718997, \"rank\": 9.980603115140778e-07, \"text\": \"Felix\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Felix_Mendelssohn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Felix_Mendelssohn\"}, {\"begin\": 2442, \"end\": 2446, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"score\": 0.9999612359330181, \"rank\": 3.876242615256982e-05, \"text\": \"Nike\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympic Nursery Experience.Shoutout to Allyson Felix manpic.twitter.com/rd1AiP0TLL  NBC, the official broadcaster of the Paris 2024 Olympics, also adapted to the changing media landscape by betting big on pop culture.\", \"from\": 2473, \"to\": 2690, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2600, \"end\": 2613, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"2024 Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Snoop Dogg's role as a special correspondent added a layer of entertainment that was unexpected and highly engaging.\", \"from\": 2691, \"to\": 2807, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2691, \"end\": 2701, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Snoop Dogg\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His spontaneous dance moves at gymnastics events, pre-filmed clips with Michael Phelps, and humorous commentary on events like badminton and rugby went viral across social media platforms.\", \"from\": 2809, \"to\": 2997, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2881, \"end\": 2895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.064406151335304e-31, \"text\": \"Michael Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The decision to integrate Snoop Dogg paid off handsomely, with the network averaging 34m viewers across its platforms in the five days following the opening ceremony-an increase of 15m from the Tokyo Games.\", \"from\": 2998, \"to\": 3204, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3024, \"end\": 3034, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Snoop Dogg\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This strategic move highlighted the growing importance of cultural relevance and entertainment in capturing audience attention, even for a traditional broadcaster like NBC.\", \"from\": 3206, \"to\": 3378, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3374, \"end\": 3377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9826829060700963, \"rank\": 0.017506069154411826, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"LA28 we ready!!!\", \"from\": 3380, \"to\": 3396, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Closing ceremony vibes wit@drdreyall \\ud83c\\uddfa\\ud83c\\uddf8\\ud83c\\uddeb\\ud83c\\uddf7\\ud83d\\udcaf\\ud83d\\udc4a\\ud83c\\udfffpic.twitter.com/sxLnlRq00Z  The Paris 2024 Olympics have shown that the future of brand sponsorship lies in digital innovation and cultural resonance.\", \"from\": 3397, \"to\": 3591, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3486, \"end\": 3499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"2024 Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As brands like Samsung, Pampers, and NBC have demonstrated, success at the Olympics now hinges on the ability to create meaningful, shareable experiences that transcend the boundaries of traditional media.\", \"from\": 3592, \"to\": 3797, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3614, \"end\": 3621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"score\": 0.9999999951623977, \"rank\": 4.8377783380414496e-09, \"text\": \"Samsung\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\"}, {\"begin\": 3623, \"end\": 3630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pampers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pampers\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pampers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pampers\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the 2028 Games on the horizon, it will be fascinating to see how these trends evolve, what new technologies emerge to shape the next generation of Olympic partnerships and how open the IOC will be to embrace them.\", \"from\": 3799, \"to\": 4017, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Share this article  Subscribe to the City AM newsletter to have our top stories delivered directly to your inbox.\", \"from\": 4019, \"to\": 4132, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow us for breaking news and latest updates\", \"from\": 4134, \"to\": 4180, \"entities\": []}]}"